    "description": "<strong>Blood of Mehran</strong> 是《天方夜谭》中的一篇，讲述了一个关于爱、失落和忠诚的故事。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714530/extras/a34ece1bb642e37067e4acee92f98ab2.poster.avif?t=1759820232\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714530/extras/a34ece1bb642e37067e4acee92f98ab2.webm?t=1759820232\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714530/extras/a34ece1bb642e37067e4acee92f98ab2.mp4?t=1759820232\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>传奇战士 Mehran 为和平放下自己的剑 — 他平静的生活被他人残酷的野心所摧毁，令他别无选择，只能再次拿起剑。<br><br>组合各种武器，在众多敌人中砍杀出一条血路：<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>剑和盾牌<br></li><li>双剑<br></li><li>弓和箭 </li></ul>或者利用直观的隐身和掩护机制像幽灵一样溜过。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714530/extras/d65600dbbaebfdef0a51e762be282877.poster.avif?t=1759820232\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714530/extras/d65600dbbaebfdef0a51e762be282877.webm?t=1759820232\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714530/extras/d65600dbbaebfdef0a51e762be282877.mp4?t=1759820232\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>探索逼真的古代美索不达米亚社会。在起伏的沙丘上驰骋，在拥挤的城市街巷中穿行。探索世界，收集物品、揭开秘密。不断升级，直至登上技能树之巅，提升英雄的传奇力量。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >回报颇丰的砍杀战斗系统</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714530/extras/5c100ba542fcefd5a7be495285aafd09.poster.avif?t=1759820232\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714530/extras/5c100ba542fcefd5a7be495285aafd09.webm?t=1759820232\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714530/extras/5c100ba542fcefd5a7be495285aafd09.mp4?t=1759820232\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >反复尝试隐身、远程和骑乘选项</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714530/extras/a77ea51e14a11ef983ca29a0c37c0871.poster.avif?t=1759820232\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714530/extras/a77ea51e14a11ef983ca29a0c37c0871.webm?t=1759820232\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714530/extras/a77ea51e14a11ef983ca29a0c37c0871.mp4?t=1759820232\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索一个充满奇迹和可收集物品的世界</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714530/extras/8ac9331c6e298ee01361cb9bdc4ad55e.poster.avif?t=1759820232\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714530/extras/8ac9331c6e298ee01361cb9bdc4ad55e.webm?t=1759820232\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714530/extras/8ac9331c6e298ee01361cb9bdc4ad55e.mp4?t=1759820232\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
